{"tid":2231251,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子中環墮樓亡　消息指為美心太子女伍淑清妹夫","createTime":"2020-10-05T13:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T05:50:54.000Z","uid":11512,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f480283d20eef467cb398d922fe9b1e80e0cb90b","tid":2231251,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"今日下午中環一名約 70 歲的男子墮樓。警方消息指，死者是美心太子女伍淑清的妹夫周裕農。<br />\n<br />\n警方證實案發在下午約 4 時 30 分，中環都爹利街 8 號香港鑽石會大廈，一名年約 70 歲的男子被發現倒臥在平台位置，當場證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方消息指，死者是美心集團女婿伍氏家族的女婿周裕農。周裕農的妻子是伍淑芬，亦即美心太子女伍淑清的妹妹。本年初有報道指，伍淑芬獲委任為美心食品母公司香港食品有限公司的候補董事。<br />\n<br />\n周裕農則是上海顏料大王周宗良的孫兒，有海外銀行背景，曾任日本東京銀行顧問、美國芝加哥第一國民銀行助理副總裁等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/maxim-06_5kWPP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmaxim-06_5kWPP_1200x0.png&h=03b34efd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36234c34fda08c2a5b1e89b0c955b28d18c1f2b7","tid":2231251,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T13:56:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"194d14903555ef70aa0fce29d7a6094d3b964930","tid":2231251,"uid":134863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"若然未報"},{"pid":"4496285a8d47c994590a7320f56f0a54ae4b0c1f","tid":2231251,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"車公：天網恢恢 疏不漏！"},{"pid":"ea37803fc2010f81257dac2506ae295aebc89503","tid":2231251,"uid":147367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"比伍淑清放棄左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb453b8db79de68aea735fb48449c9ced959ace","tid":2231251,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"搵cctvb打電話問下伍婆心情係點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996340ae48f015b8ad0d97280ab8103e